div.div:
The transaction between the configuration widget and the diagram editor is minimal.
From the editor:
- Path of loaded Modelica libraries and user working directory
- Modelica code of the currently edited model
From the widget:
- Path of configured model (so the editor can reload it after update)

The configuration widget needs to translate:
- From Modelica to JSON: all models referenced in the configuration data file and the currently edited model if it contains __Linkage_data annotation.
- from JSON to Modelica: the output model resulting from the configuration model builder.
